# campaign-condition-system

Multi-Stage Condition Engine:
- Sequential condition evaluation with dependency chains
- Parallel condition tracking for multiple reward paths
- Time-based condition triggers with delay support
- Condition grouping with AND/OR logic

Reward Trigger System:
- Multi-type reward provisioning (gift cards, SMS, webhooks)
- Inventory pool management for reward fulfillment
- Delivery method selection based on recipient preferences
- Automated retry logic for failed deliveries

Action Sequence Handler:
- Ordered action execution with prerequisite validation
- Rollback support for failed action chains
- Event logging for condition completions
- Integration points for external systems (CRM, SMS, email)

